channel.title: Cold Transmissions from the Axoloti
channel.description:
I've started a small, intended-to-be-infrequent video series documenting my patches. All of these patches are from recording sessions for upcoming EPs.
Nothing groundbreaking, but it has been fun documenting specific patches/sounds! Great way to demo the Axoloti for my classes, too!
[Cold Transmissions from the Axoloti #1](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4HNva9Va0qc)
